1.5 Decorrelating using IDeA

1.7.2 Univariate t-test


tvals <- function(x,target)
{
  lmt <- lm(target~x)
  sm <- summary(lmt)
  return(sm$coefficients[2,3])
}

rawunittvalues <- apply(testingset[,names(outcomeModel$coef)[-1]],2,tvals,testingset[,outcome])
deunittvalues <- apply(testage_DE[,names(outcomeModel_DE$coef)[-1]],2,tvals,testingset[,outcome])

1.7.3 Comparing summaries


psig <- 0.05/(ncol(testingset)-1)

smcoef$Uni_t_values <- rawunittvalues[rownames(smcoef)]

     main="Raw: Univariate t-values vs regression t-values",

     ylim=xvals
     )
